    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Belts that are intended to be worn through loops sewn to a pair of trousers to secure them to the waist of the wearer. These may be made from a variety of materials, and usually are secured with an adjustable buckle or some other fastener.</Note_Text>
